{"title":"隐私泛滥","authors":["池北偶江帆"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":1,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"隐私泛滥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗江帆画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生道路各异，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隐私人皆有之。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本来不可告人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今争相揭秘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷自我炒作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"著书风行一时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随便加油添醋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总要抹粉涂脂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至任意编造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噱头光怪陆离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说尽风流韵事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做爱也成话题。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文字不够刺激，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"图片可增魅力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人爱看内幕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人喜听隐私，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写的绘声绘色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读的如醉如痴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽量投其所好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你开卷我收益。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}